  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/64f921bbb7993edff3e14ec5b2541608.avif?t=1762526133\" width=900 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shadow Falls is an emotionally charged horror game where a grieving mother ventures into a forest to scatter her son's ashes, only to be drawn to an isolated farmhouse where strange things start to unfold. As she uncovers the secrets of the house and the forest, she discovers that death might not be the end and is faced with a harrowing choice that requires the ultimate sacrifice. Her journey explores the depths of a mother's unconditional love and the lengths she will go to for her child, all while battling malevolent entities determined to preserve the natural order and prevent her from reuniting with her son.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/8f05fb2ce553f6bdcf735afcb1eb95d1.avif?t=1762526133\" width=900 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse the breathtaking landscapes of Shadow Falls National Park, from the dense forest to the enigmatic old farmhouse and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/1f96e918921ee5ec3d091401accc7784.poster.avif?t=1762526133\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/1f96e918921ee5ec3d091401accc7784.webm?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/1f96e918921ee5ec3d091401accc7784.mp4?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/f232d85d850453203fc943a826d5c83d.avif?t=1762526133\" width=900 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather clues and unravel puzzles and riddles to advance your quest and uncover the secrets of Shadow Falls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/68e9e7fe6e2d0d187a083687513d8c6d.poster.avif?t=1762526133\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/68e9e7fe6e2d0d187a083687513d8c6d.webm?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/68e9e7fe6e2d0d187a083687513d8c6d.mp4?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/a893880500d238e9b4e06a514778608d.avif?t=1762526133\" width=900 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect notes that delve into the rich backstory of Shadow Falls and its enigmatic residents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/aec24b5dc69fa57b9b15ea5d7ef72a46.poster.avif?t=1762526133\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/aec24b5dc69fa57b9b15ea5d7ef72a46.webm?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/aec24b5dc69fa57b9b15ea5d7ef72a46.mp4?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/0fdb718031496b6526082ef43c8ef5cb.avif?t=1762526133\" width=900 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire a unique collection of artifacts essential for conducting the ultimate séance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/343d5acab9da628fdde535ea58e89b35.poster.avif?t=1762526133\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/343d5acab9da628fdde535ea58e89b35.webm?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/343d5acab9da628fdde535ea58e89b35.mp4?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/2a211d5288397ea0d5e5576f2722d124.avif?t=1762526133\" width=900 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage with NPCs, encountering both allies and adversaries along your journey</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/6876784556a8fecd39a9a777fd44bfab.poster.avif?t=1762526133\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/6876784556a8fecd39a9a777fd44bfab.webm?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/6876784556a8fecd39a9a777fd44bfab.mp4?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/64f921bbb7993edff3e14ec5b2541608.avif?t=1762526133\" width=900 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shadow Falls is an emotionally charged horror game where a grieving mother ventures into a forest to scatter her son's ashes, only to be drawn to an isolated farmhouse where strange things start to unfold. As she uncovers the secrets of the house and the forest, she discovers that death might not be the end and is faced with a harrowing choice that requires the ultimate sacrifice. Her journey explores the depths of a mother's unconditional love and the lengths she will go to for her child, all while battling malevolent entities determined to preserve the natural order and prevent her from reuniting with her son.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/8f05fb2ce553f6bdcf735afcb1eb95d1.avif?t=1762526133\" width=900 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse the breathtaking landscapes of Shadow Falls National Park, from the dense forest to the enigmatic old farmhouse and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/1f96e918921ee5ec3d091401accc7784.poster.avif?t=1762526133\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/1f96e918921ee5ec3d091401accc7784.webm?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621480/extras/1f96e918921ee5ec3d091401accc7784.mp4?t=1762526133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></vi